{"tid":2255510,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今次空姐災難，仁安同逸東，仲有識好多小店同表示施予援手，次次有事都係民間自救，冇政府香港人活得更好","createTime":"2020-10-23T14:59:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-23T17:39:34.000Z","uid":31215,"like":39,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"fc56f3451351a441876552af90fe3fbdf52a698c","tid":2255510,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T14:59:52.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<br />\n港共淨係識迫害市民<br />\n有事就靠唔住<br />\n淨係同你計民生嗰part<br />\n市民要口罩嗰時，維基整緊口罩機，市民入緊海外口罩<br />\n政府係叫人唔好戴口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到大家口罩充足，先整利益輸送口罩，仲要柒又要洗，一人一盒仲平仲實用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要冇乜人攞<br />\n<br />\n搞搞疫基金<br />\n派錢俾老闆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後送錢救國泰，救到港龍都執埋<br />\n呢筆錢攞嚟開公營事業請空姐仲有用<br />\n<br />\n我屌你老母港共<br />\n淨係識迫害香港人<br />\n香港人架空政府算9數啦"},{"pid":"c8309295bbb5cdd545d902a968187ea799fc6a34","tid":2255510,"uid":231583,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T15:00:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ba9f86d50a31b77c9502acd28054b952a43443de","tid":2255510,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c8309295bbb5cdd545d902a968187ea799fc6a34","tid":2255510,"uid":231583,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T15:00:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T15:01:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd93e25e59f9c0923ebcc2ea11112202444ebeff","tid":2255510,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T15:02:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"497d3d4593be76056a1e6813a83aca2b9598641b","tid":2255510,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T15:04:11.000Z","msg":"屌你老母死港共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1291debc95e8dd584c6b8ae811b49ad